## Include Stratejisi

Policy için gerekli ilişkileri tek sorguda `include`/`select` ile al — N+1 yasak değil ama gereksiz full graph çekme.

Character read: `campaign` + `campaign.members` gerekebilir. Campaign read: `members` zorunlu.

## Character Policy Örneği

```typescript
static canRead(user: AuthUser | null, character: CharacterWithRelations): boolean {
  if (user?.role === Role.ADMIN) return true;
  if (character.visibility === CharacterVisibility.PUBLIC) return true;
  if (!user) return false;
  if (character.ownerId === user.id) return true;
  if (character.campaignId && character.campaign) {
    if (character.campaign.ownerId === user.id) return true;
    return character.campaign.members.some((m) => m.userId === user.id);
  }
  return false;
}

static canWrite(user: AuthUser, character: CharacterWithRelations): boolean {
  if (user.role === Role.ADMIN) return true;
  if (character.ownerId === user.id) return true;
  if (character.campaignId && character.campaign?.ownerId === user.id) return true;
  return false;
}
```

`canUpdateVisibility` — yalnızca owner (DM değil) — ayrı method veya `Action.UPDATE_VISIBILITY`.

## Homebrew Policy Örneği

```typescript
static canRead(user: AuthUser | null, item: HomebrewItem): boolean {
  if (user?.role === Role.ADMIN) return true;
  if (item.status === HomebrewStatus.PUBLISHED) return true;
  if (!user) return false;
  return item.ownerId === user.id;
}

static canWrite(user: AuthUser, item: HomebrewItem): boolean {
  if (user.role === Role.ADMIN) return true;
  return item.ownerId === user.id;
}
```

Official seed (`source = OFFICIAL`) — user write policy false (admin path ayrı).

