| Resource | null user read |
| --- | --- |
| Reference | ✅ Public |
| Homebrew PUBLISHED | ✅ |
| Character PUBLIC | ✅ |
| Campaign | ❌ |
| Character PRIVATE | ❌ |
| Homebrew DRAFT | ❌ |

